Package main.model.camp

Class Camp

java.lang.Object
main.model.camp.Camp
All Implemented Interfaces:
Displayable, Model, Mappable
public class Camp extends Object implements Model, Displayable
Represents a camp, including its status, ID, staff, students, title, faculty, location, description, maximum slots, available slots and related functionalities
